      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nthere is the reason to essentially prevent access to some objects by others because the object can be used in different stacks. using NO_CACHE flag doesn't help in that case and will be another consequences like MDT finding an object with no appropriate slices..",
